OL,3,CFour more people arrested as murder
OL,4,Cinvestigation continues
OL,6,FA further four people have been
OL,7,Farrested as detectives continue to
OL,8,Finvestigate the death of a man in
OL,9,FMiddlesbrough.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to
OL,12,FAyton Crescent in Eston at around 11pm
OL,13,Fon Saturday night (23 May). They found
OL,14,Fa man who was then pronounced dead at
OL,15,Fthe scene.
OL,17,FOn Monday, Cleveland Police confirmed
OL,18,Fa 39-year-old man had been arrested on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
