OL,3,CFour more people arrested as murder
OL,4,Cinvestigation continues
OL,6,FA 65-year-old man has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of assisting an offender and
OL,8,Fobstructing a constable.
OL,10,FTwo women, aged 67 and 28, were both
OL,11,Farrested on suspicion of assisting an
OL,12,Foffender.
OL,14,FThis follows the arrest of a 38-year-
OL,15,Fold woman on Sunday (24 May) on
OL,16,Fsuspicion of assisting an offender and
OL,17,Fconspiring to commit murder. All
OL,18,Fremain in police custody at this time.
OL,20,FFlowers have been left at the scene in
OL,21,FAyton Crescent.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
