OL,3,CFour more people arrested as murder
OL,4,Cinvestigation continues
OL,6,FSuperintendent Daryll Tomlinson said:
OL,7,F"We are continuing our investigation
OL,8,Ftoday and have made four further
OL,9,Farrests. There will be an increased
OL,10,Fpresence in the area with visible
OL,11,Fpatrols from our officers.
OL,13,F"If you have any information that
OL,14,Fcould assist this investigation,
OL,15,Fplease contact Cleveland Police on
OL,16,F101, quoting reference number 098497,
OL,17,For report anonymously via
OL,18,FCrimestoppers."
